track.name: Better Days (NEIKED x Mae Muller x Polo G)

album.title: Better Days (NEIKED x Mae Muller x Polo G)

wiki.summary: Swedish producer NEIKED recruits rap icon, Polo G and up and coming singer, Mae Muller for a collaborative pop song. The song went viral online amassing over 180,000 videos made with the song on the video-sharing platform, Tik Tok. The song has gone on to have massive chart success debuting on the Billboard Top 100 at #57 and peaking at #29, this being Mullers first Billboard chart entry. Better Days has also charted on the Official Charts peaking at #32. The song’s success also caused Mae to become the December 2021 Billboard Chart Breaker. Read more on Last.fm.
